'''阿拉－恰普拉大桥''' （{{lang-hi|आरा-छपरा सेतु}}）或称'''维尔·孔瓦尔·辛格大桥'''（{{lang-hi|वीर कुँवर सिंह सेतु}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/1170611/jsp/frontpage/story_156221.jsp|title=Bridge opening boon for north Bihar link|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107011755/https://www.telegraphindia.com/1170611/jsp/frontpage/story_156221.jsp|archivedate=2017-11-07}}</ref>，是[[印度|印度]][[比哈尔邦|比哈尔邦]]一座[[公路|公路]][[桥梁|桥梁]]，跨越[[恒河|恒河]]，连接[[波吉布尔县|波吉布尔县]]的[[阿拉_(印度)|阿拉]]与[[萨兰县|萨兰县]]的[[恰普拉|恰普拉]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1101230/jsp/bihar/story_13369018.jsp|title=Ganga link to connect Ara & Chhapra|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2010-12-30|author=Rakesh K. Singh|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-date=2012-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120520070513/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1101230/jsp/bihar/story_13369018.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1160613/jsp/bihar/story_90847.jsp#.V_ktTOV97IU|title=Land bids put bridges in troubled waters|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2016-06-13|author=Piyush Kumar Tripathi|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-date=2016-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009181813/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1160613/jsp/bihar/story_90847.jsp#.V_ktTOV97IU|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该桥建成后成为连接比哈尔邦南北方一条重要的公路通道<ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/Ara-Chhapra-road-bridge-on-Ganga-river-to-be-ready-by-June-2016/articleshow/50336830.cms|title=Ara-Chhapra road bridge on Ganga river to be ready by June 2016|last=Kumar|first=Madan|date=2015-12-26|publisher=The Times of India|location=Patna, India|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-date=2015-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151227185754/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/Ara-Chhapra-road-bridge-on-Ganga-river-to-be-ready-by-June-2016/articleshow/50336830.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 设计和建造 ==
大桥采用[[设计－建造|设计－建造]]总承包模式修建，全长约{{convert|4.35|km|0}}，其中跨河主桥部分长{{convert|1920|m|0}}，主梁为等高单箱单室[[箱梁|箱梁]]，采用平衡悬臂拼装法施工；桥墩为双薄壁墩，两墩壁间距为{{convert|3|m|0}}，桥[[基础|基础]]采用沉井基础<ref name="sjql">{{cite journal|author=张妮|date=2016|title=印度阿拉-恰布拉恒河大桥|journal=世界桥梁|publisher=中铁大桥局集团有限公司|location=武汉|volume=44|issue=5|pages=95-96|issn=1671-7767|url=http://www.xueshu.com/sjql/201605/27578862.html|access-date=2017-02-07|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207192619/http://www.xueshu.com/sjql/201605/27578862.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 项目 ==
阿拉－恰普拉大桥建成后，恰普拉与阿拉之间的路程从{{convert|120|km|0}}缩短至{{convert|20|km|0}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.livehindustan.com/news/patna/article1-%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%83%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF-%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87-%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE-%E0%A4%B5-%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE-%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%81%E0%A5%9C%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%87-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%9C%E0%A4%95-%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%97-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87-647888.html|title=भोजपुरिया संस्कृति वाले छपरा व आरा जुड़ेंगे सड़क मार्ग से|publisher=Hindustan|date=2016-12-30|author=नई उम्मीद|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-date=2017-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102123650/http://www.livehindustan.com/news/patna/article1-%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%83%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF-%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87-%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE-%E0%A4%B5-%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE-%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%81%E0%A5%9C%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%87-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%9C%E0%A4%95-%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%97-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87-647888.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这大大缩短了从[[锡万|锡万]]、恰普拉、[[戈帕尔甘杰县|戈帕尔甘杰县]]到阿拉、[[奥兰加巴德县|奥兰加巴德县]]和[[开姆尔县|开姆尔县]]的距离<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.livehindustan.com/news/patna/article1-New-road-conecting-north-and-south-bihar-571441.html|title=उत्तर और दक्षिण बिहार जुड़ जाएगा नई सड़क से आरा-छपरा के बीच बन रहा नया पुल शुरू हो जाएगा|publisher=Hindustan|date=2016-10-04|author=पटना। हिन्दुस्तान ब्यूरो|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-date=2016-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008081913/http://www.livehindustan.com/news/patna/article1-New-road-conecting-north-and-south-bihar-571441.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；比哈尔邦内的南北交通可不必绕行[[巴特那县|巴特那县]]。大桥设四车道公路，在恰普拉与19号国道相接，在阿拉的[[科伊尔瓦尔|科伊尔瓦尔]]与30号国道相接<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jagran.com/bihar/bhojpur-12668612.html|title=संस्कृति को सशक्त करेगा आरा-छपरा पुल|publisher=Jagran|date=2015-07-30|author=|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-date=2016-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009185322/http://www.jagran.com/bihar/bhojpur-12668612.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1131016/jsp/bihar/story_17456247.jsp#.V_ktNuV97IU|title=Expressway extension wish on CM lips|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2013-10-16|author=|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-date=2016-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009181421/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1131016/jsp/bihar/story_17456247.jsp#.V_ktNuV97IU|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年7月，{{le|比哈尔邦首席部长|List of Chief Ministers of Bihar}}{{le|尼蒂什·库玛尔|Nitish Kumar}}为大桥奠基，他宣称自己的愿望是连通整个[[比哈尔语|比哈尔语]]地区。

2015年4月25日，[[2015年4月尼泊尔地震|尼泊尔发生7.8级地震]]时，大桥下部施工已经完成，上部结构正在修建，桥址距离[[震中|震中]]约{{convert|300|km|0}}，施工没有受到很大影响<ref name="sjql" />。

2015年9月，大桥建筑工地发生[[起重机|起重机]]倒塌事故，造成7人死亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ani/seven-killed-after-crane-collapses-at-arrah-chapra-bridge-construction-site-115091400682_1.html|title=Seven killed after crane collapses at Arrah-Chapra bridge construction site|publisher=Business Standard News|date=2015-09-14|author=|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-date=2016-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313033429/http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ani/seven-killed-after-crane-collapses-at-arrah-chapra-bridge-construction-site-115091400682_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

